1. DEFINITIONS
================================================================================

"Software" means the source code, build scripts, UI, and original application
assets in this repository (excluding Third-Party Data).

"Third-Party Data" means prayer time schedules, Qur'an text and page layout
data, Qur'an recitation audio, and any other content obtained from external
sources, including but not limited to:

  - Bang Kurdistan (prayer times)
    https://github.com/Bang-Kurdistan

  - QUL / Tarteel AI resources (Qur'an page and text layout data)
    https://qul.tarteel.ai/resources/

  - EveryAyah (Qur'an recitation audio)
    https://everyayah.com/


